---
// Footer.astro
// Clean, low-contrast footer carrying copyright, philosophy and brand signature.
---

<footer class="bg-canvas border-t border-hairline py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="font-display text-sm font-bold tracking-[1.5px] text-white">
          BYTE TRUE
        </span>
        <span class="text-xs text-muted font-display tracking-[0.5px]">
          // TECH DEMOCRATIZATION
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted font-body max-w-md">
        Lowering the barriers of complex, high-ceiling innovations so that they become accessible, stable, and practical for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:items-end gap-2 text-xs font-display tracking-[0.5px] text-muted">
      <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} BYTE TRUE. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</span>
      <span>BUILT WITH ASTRO + TAILWIND CSS</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
